IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. "io-demo".
AUTHOR. "CENTRA-NF v0.4.0".

ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
OS "Linux".
ARCH "x86_64".
RUNTIME-VERSION "0.4.0".

DATA DIVISION.
    INPUT AS VIDEO-MP4.
    OUTPUT AS VIDEO-MP4.
    MESSAGE AS BINARY-BLOB.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    DISPLAY "CENTRA-NF v0.4.0 I/O Operations Demo".
    DISPLAY "===================================".

    DISPLAY "Testing DISPLAY instruction:".
    DISPLAY "Hello, World from CENTRA-NF!".

    DISPLAY "Testing PRINT instruction:".
    PRINT MESSAGE.

    DISPLAY "Testing PRINT with format:".
    PRINT MESSAGE WITH "Message content: ".

    DISPLAY "Demo completed successfully!".